OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy start with a little
OL,6,Frain. Then becoming drier with a few
OL,7,Fbright or sunny intervals and just the
OL,8,Fodd shower. Fresh to strong southerly
OL,9,Fwinds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA dry start to the evening
OL,12,Fthen a band of rain crossing Orkney
OL,13,Fmid evening then Shetland around
OL,14,Fmidnight, followed by clearer weather
OL,15,Fwith scattered showers. Southerly
OL,16,Fgales.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
