OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FShowers will become more
OL,6,Ffrequent during the morning, then more
OL,7,Fscattered later with more in the way
OL,8,Fof sunshine. Strong to gale southerly
OL,9,Fwinds veering westerly, perhaps severe
OL,10,Fbriefly.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FA
OL,13,Fvery showery few days the showers most
OL,14,Ffrequent and heavy on Thursday when
OL,15,Fthere will be southwesterly gales.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
